### Versions
- Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore 9.0.6
- Npgsql.EntityFrameworkCore.PostgreSQL 9.0.4
- .NET 9.0.205

(I also ran into this on Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore 9.0.4 and 9.0.3, so the issue isn't caused by the mismatch between Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore 9.0.6 and Npgsql.EntityFrameworkCore.PostgreSQL 9.0.4. These are just the latest non-preview versions as of me setting up this repro sample and writing this description.)
